title: Olivia Munn Wants Wonder Woman to Suck It
description:
Okay okay I know we’re starting to sound like the podcasters who cried why does this book exist but… why does this book exist. In an effort to better understand the rebound girlfriend of the century Claire and Ashley open up Olivia Munn’s ode to geekdom to discover that Olivia Munn has no idea what a geek even is.
